com.amplifyframework.core.model

Class ModelAssociation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.core.model.ModelAssociation

  • public final class ModelAssociation
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an association of the Model class. This class encapsulates the information provided by the following annotations on model fields: - BelongsTo - HasOne - HasMany Only @BelongsTo tag implies that the field is a foreign key.
